<h3>Roadmap</h3>

<p>Swift hopes to engage self-interested teams of “citizen editors” who curate publicly available information about an event (partircularly a crisis) as it happens. Swift is currently a work in progress and has not reached a releasable state. The near-term technical goal of Swift is to provide an API (for programmers) and data set (for researchers) about an arbitrary set of RSS feeds. Check out the <a href="http://groups.google.com/group/swiftriver">general discussion list</a> and <a href="http://groups.google.com/group/swift-dev">the developer list</a> if you are interested in seeing how progress is going. 
